@bewing Many thanks for the suggestion! The following code did the trick...
```python
           try:
                lldp_table.GET_RPC = 'get-lldp-interface-neighbors-information'
                lldp_table.get(interface_name=interface)
            except (RpcError, IOError) as e:
                if isinstance(e, IOError) and not inspect.trace()[-1][3] == "find_file":
                    # Only accept an IOError from BaseTestDouble.find_file
                    raise e
                lldp_table.GET_RPC = 'get-lldp-interface-neighbors'
                lldp_table.get(interface_device=interface)
```
